                          Angular-front end technology             
                          ------------------------------

                                   Basic Commands
                                   -----------------


                    1.creation of angular project-ng new project-name   

                    2.to runangular project -ng serve

                    3.component creation -ng g c component-name

                    4.service creation - ng g s servic-name



                                    Basic Component
                                    ----------------



                    1.Module -To import 3rd party library - root module(defaultly)-AppModule

                    2.Components -html,css,ts

                    3.To set up path for component -App Routing module file

                    4.routing-outlet selector (show user request html page to browser) 

                    5.Angular Service(for api calling or service calling)   

                    6.Dependency Injection(data share in angular) it perform always inside constuctor(here we use constructor only for dependency injection)
                                          syntax: access-specifier(public/private/protect) object-name:dependent class-name


                    7.asynchronous -rxjs -observable(typescript resolve asynchronous function) - here resolve by using subscribe instead of then(here expect a call back function)      


                8.Data Binding -sharing data inside a component   

                      8.1 One way Binding 

                         8.1.1 component(ts file) to view(html)

                             8.1.1.1 String Interpolation(ts file defined variable wnt to show in html file, variabl name define in double{{}}) -{{variable-name}}

                             8.1.1.2 property Binding -[attribute]="property-name" (proprty define in ts can see in html as attribute)

                         8.1.2 view to component

                             8.1.2.1 Event Binding -(event)="function-call" ---(html file) (fuction definition ts file) html to ts binding
                             8.1.2.2 Event Binding using $event-(event)="function-call($event)
                             8.1.2.3 Template Reference Variable

                      8.2 Two Way Binding 

                         8.2.1 ngModel (Template Driven Forms-first design html file so it in driven forms)   

                           - FormsModule(we have to import FormsModule)  [(ngModule)]="variable-name" 
                           -ngSubmit - apply it in form tag ,(ngSubmit)="fuction call" 


                9. Angular Directive -to manipulate DOM

                    9.1 Component Directive

                    9.2 Structural Direactive -if we want to add or remove new html elements in dom based any condition  we use structural directive  ,it is preceeded by * sign

                        9.2.1  *ngIf="condition" - (for providing condition ,it is in any html element)  

                        9.2.2  *ngFor="let variable-name of array-name"     
                          
                
                10. ActivatedRoute -provides access to information about a route assocciated with a component

                11.Router  class -use navigateByUrl()  to navigate one page another using ts


                12. pipe-to convert user input to another format
                                      